Family (2 adults 2 teenager) Two day in HoiAn area
Aug 2018 • Family
Vu was our tour guide in Hoi An area. We had one day with a car visiting the Myson sanctuary and military museum in Hoi An, and one day we had a bike tour around Hoi An. Vu has deep knowledge of the area, history, religion and culture. He shared his knowledge with excellent communication skills in English and his attitude in these days made it a memorable experience we will cherish. Highly recommended.
