Review of: Marble mountain and Linh Ung temple from Da Nang/ Hoi An (4 hour)
Written February 27, 2024
Aurindam k
Excellent food tour experience in Hoi An
Friendly & Interactive. We experienced the traditional food prepared by the local families at their home & also at eating joints that are a famous for their unique recipes introduced by their previous generations.
The tour was perfect for us, where we experimented with a lot of Vietnamese food items & especially some which are found only in Hoi An. Vu also made sure we know the story and history behind the food we tasted and relished.
Definitely worth it!
